snippet.textDisplay:
According to me Coke studio is a very advanced musical platform, and we as commoners really don't have much knowledge in judging their music. The way coke studio experiments with songs and the music Dynamics and singers is amazing. I have enjoyed all songs till now. I believe coke studio produces 3 main kinds of songs 
1. Songs which are instantly catchy- afreen from season 9 
2. Songs which grow on you - khaki banda from season 9
 3. Songs which people crtisize but are actually new experiments. - sayonee or alahu Akbar this season 
 We should listen to coke studio with the thought of learning and we will never be disappointed on the other hand we will feel enriched with the music knowledge we gained.
Kudos to coke studio keep bringing us great music for years to come.

Sorry for the long winding comment but I wanted to get this thought out there.
